description: When Northern California is in need of a little Southern comfort, in rolls Rollin Roadhouse, and it doesn’t hold back when it comes to bringing the best BBQ to Sacramento. You can find this truck ridin’ around town, rollin’ out bonafide sliders, slow-roasted meats, all complete with their signature homemade BBQ sauce. And of course, as you’d expect in America’s Farm-to-Fork capital, Rollin Roadhouse is rockin’ it with their home-smoked pork.  For some quality comfort cuisine, make it a goal to hit up Rollin Roadhouse.
name: Rollin Roadhouse
